Package: R.MFIV
Title: Calculate Model Free Implied Volatility, i.e. the CBOE VIX from Option Quotes
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Martin Georg",
           family = "Haas",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "haasmartin@live.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0977-0939"))
Description: Provides functions to calculate the CBOE VIX, intermediary values 
    and the Jiang & Tian (2007) smoothing method to deal with an insufficient 
    strike price range.
URL: https://github.com/m-g-h/R.MFIV
